	<p pid="a.180.1/1">asked Her Majesty's Government:</p>
	<p pid="a.180.1/2" qnum="HL5945">Whether, with the agreement of Professor Tony Atkinson of Nuffield College, they will take responsibility for the ongoing publication of his top 1 per cent. of income earners series alongside currently published series for deciles and quartiles.</p>
