	<p pid="a.180.2/1">The latest information on the share of income of the top 1 per cent. of taxpayers is available in table 2.4, &quot;Shares of total income (before and after tax) and income tax for percentile groups&quot; which is available on the HM Revenue and Customs website at <a href="http://www.hmrc.gov.uk/stats/incometax/table24.xls">www.hmrc.gov.uk/stats/income tax/table2 4.xls</a>. HMRC has no current plans to produce any further analyses beyond those already published.</p>
